                  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">
                    <tr>
                      <td><font size="3">Pitcairn</font></td>
                      <td align="right"><font size="3"><img src="../../img/flags/flg_pitcairn.gif" width="70" height="35"></font></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" height="1">
                    <tr background="../../img/maps/cp_tile.gif" valign="top"> 
                      <td background="../../img/maps/cp_tile.gif"><img src="../../img/maps/cp_space.gif" width="37" height="1"></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <p class="profile_intro">The island of Pitcairn is the last 
                    colonial outpost of Britain in the Pacific. Its inhabitants 
                    are direct descendants of the mutineers of the Bounty and 
                    their Tahitian wives. 
                  <p align="center"><img src="../../img/maps/cp_pitcairn.gif" width="480" height="326" alt="Map of Pitcairn"></p>
                  <h5><a name="facts"></a>Facts and Figures</h5>
